Package: eneRgetics
Title: Estimates the Maintenance Metabolism of shorebirds
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Carneiro", "Camilo", , "camilofcarneiro@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Correia", "Ricardo", role = "aut"),
    person("Alves", "JosÃ© A.", role = "aut")
  )
Description: eneRgetics provides a fast and straightforward way to calculate the
    Maintenance Metabolism of shorebirds. It has functions to retrieve the necessary
    environmental data to calculate it, to retrieve tidal data and to create
    categories for the tide state in relation to low tide. Additionally, it provides
    a function to calculate the Basal Metabolic Rate of shorebirds.
